snippet: Health insurance executives summoned to a House hearing Wednesday refused to go along with any G.O.P criticism of the health care law, undercutting some arguments against it.
abstract: Half-dozen health insurance executives summoned to House hearing refuse to go along with any Republican criticism of the health care law, undercutting some of lawmakers' arguments against it; predictions of fallout from law continue to fail to materialize.
